fields.description: Has a sweet temperament, loyal, loving, and independent.
Outgoing, gentle, very intelligent and listens well, loves being in the water.
Cheerful, alert and attentive, very active and affectionate.
Dignified, intelligent, loyal, and is strong willed.
Outgoing, determined, gets along with other dogs well, has a strong desire to please.
Enthusiastic, great with kids, smart, alert, and strong willed.
